73
00:04:42,365 --> 00:04:43,825
<i>I'm not suited for this.</i>

74
00:04:44,117 --> 00:04:47,412
<i>But it's still part of
the mission to catch Kira...</i>

75
00:04:47,954 --> 00:04:48,997
