to meet Kira.

104
00:06:18,086 --> 00:06:20,755
Wh-Who did you hear that from?

105
00:06:20,839 --> 00:06:22,632
We can't tell you our source.

106
00:06:23,008 --> 00:06:26,052
But this is reliable information.

107
00:06:26,177 --> 00:06:29,222
