don't want anyone to know...

112
00:06:46,698 --> 00:06:50,118
<i>I've got to sweat a lot
and pause here...</i>

113
00:06:50,911 --> 00:06:53,580
Misa Amane was detained by L...

114
00:06:53,997 --> 00:06:57,334
