Misa can see me again...</i>

136
00:08:24,254 --> 00:08:26,548
<i>W- What is this?! A monster?</i>

137
00:08:26,631 --> 00:08:33,555
Misa, you're in a dangerous situation.
The people from Yotsuba may kill you.

138
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:35,932
I came to tell you that.

139
00:08:36,474 --> 00:08:37,976
Calm down and listen to me.

140
00:08:38,476 --> 00:08:39,894
<i>Calm down?</i>

141
00:08:40,103 --> 00:08:42,731
