143
00:08:46,151 --> 00:08:49,237
<i>My... ally?</i>

144
00:08:50,113 --> 00:08:52,532
I wonder if Misa-Misa is all right...

145
00:08:52,866 --> 00:08:56,202
We should have at least wired her!

146
00:08:57,454 --> 00:08:59,205
<i>It's just as I thought...
They're deﬁnitely different people...</i>

147
00:08:59,748 --> 00:09:04,669
<i>The Kira before and after
I was detained... are clearly different.</i>

148
00:09:05,336 --> 00:09:06,546
<i>The current Kira is
killing off every criminal...</i>

149
00:09:06,629 --> 00:09:08,757
<i>as soon as they've had
their crime broadcast,</i>

150
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,675
<i>regardless of the situation...</i>

151
00:09:11,217 --> 00:09:14,095
<i>The previous Kira
would never punish...</i>

152
00:09:14,179 --> 00:09:17,098
<i>those who didn't have
any intention to kill,</i>

153
00:09:17,182 --> 00:09:21,978
<i>those who killed by accident, or those
with extenuating circumstances...</i>

154
00:09:23,271 --> 00:09:26,357
<i>If I were Kira,
that's what I would do...</i>

155
00:09:26,858 --> 00:09:29,611
<i>The previous Kira's
criteria for killing...</i>

156
00:09:29,694 --> 00:09:32,155
<i>are disturbingly close
to my own ideals...</i>

157
00:09:35,867 --> 00:09:37,786
<i>What am I thinking?</i>

158
00:09:38,703 --> 00:09:40,497
<i>I'm not Kira.</i>

159
00:09:40,705 --> 00:09:44,250
<i>I must be crazy to be
comparing myself to Kira...</i>

160
00:09:45,376 --> 00:09:47,045
Light Yagami is Kira.

161
00:09:48,671 --> 00:09:51,174
What is Light doing now?

162
00:10:00,391 --> 00:10:01,726
What are you?

163
00:10:02,435 --> 00:10:06,856
I know you're not a stalker,
but you don't look human at all...

164
00:10:07,273 --> 00:10:10,860
Of course. I'm a Shinigami.

165
00:10:12,195 --> 00:10:15,782
Misa, we once worked together.

166
00:10:16,282 --> 00:10:18,576
I don't know what
you're talking about...

167
00:10:19,035 --> 00:10:21,746
You met me? Light is Kira?

168
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:24,415
The Death Note...

169
00:10:26,251 --> 00:10:32,549
If you write a person's name in it,
that person dies...

170
00:10:33,758 --> 00:10:35,051
With that notebook,

171
00:10:35,135 --> 00:10:40,431
Light Yagami punished criminals
and became known as Kira.

172
00:10:43,935 --> 00:10:49,566
And you had the same... no,
greater power than Kira.

173
00:10:50,692 --> 00:10:55,947
With that power you succeeded in
getting close to Light Yagami.

174
00:10:56,656 --> 00:11:00,201
Light is Kira...
and I'm the Second Kira?

175
00:11:00,618 --> 00:11:03,830
That's right...
No, more correctly, you were.

176
00:11:04,622 --> 00:11:09,210
This should all be going
according to Light's plan.

177
00:11:10,295 --> 00:11:12,714
<i>So Ryuzaki's right!</i>

178
00:11:14,174 --> 00:11:17,969
Misa... Do you still love Light
more than anything?

179
00:11:21,389 --> 00:11:24,475
Shinigami, you really are
the real thing.

180
00:11:24,809 --> 00:11:27,020
You know everything about me.

181
00:11:27,478 --> 00:11:29,480
I'll believe everything you say...

182
00:11:30,565 --> 00:11:33,860
Yes... I love him... more than anything.

183
00:11:34,569 --> 00:11:41,326
Besides, it's really awesome
that Light and I were both Kira.

184
00:11:41,743 --> 00:11:42,785
I believe you!

185
00:11:43,453 --> 00:11:45,830
You haven't changed at all, Misa...

186
00:11:46,372 --> 00:11:50,084
Those feelings towards Light will
probably never change, will they?

187
00:11:50,585 --> 00:11:57,342
I now believe that you'll find
happiness by staying with Light.

188
00:11:57,842 --> 00:11:59,677
Thank you, Shinigami.

189
00:12:00,178 --> 00:12:01,179
It's Rem.

190
00:12:01,429 --> 00:12:04,349
The current Kira is a crooked
and pathetic human.

191
00:12:04,891 --> 00:12:08,353
You don't know what he'll do.
Be careful.

192
00:12:08,686 --> 00:12:10,688
