the other Yotsuba men, as well.

193
00:12:11,189 --> 00:12:14,234
<i>Trust Light and let him do
whatever he feels necessary.</i>

194
00:12:15,068 --> 00:12:19,030
<i>All right, I just have to
act normal, right?</i>

195
00:12:19,364 --> 00:12:20,365
<i>That's right.</i>

196
00:12:20,823 --> 00:12:23,076
<i>When you go back to the interview,</i>

197
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:28,289
<i>you should be able to tell who's Kira.
Do not trust him...</i>

198
00:12:29,707 --> 00:12:32,210
Sorry I took so long in the restroom.

199
00:12:32,627 --> 00:12:34,754
I fixed up my makeup.

200
00:12:36,422 --> 00:12:42,553
<i>All right, when you return, the man
who's sitting in front of me is Kira.</i>

201
00:12:42,929 --> 00:12:43,930
<i>Rem...</i>

202
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:46,516
<i>The person in front of Rem is Kira...</i>

203
00:12:56,442 --> 00:12:57,986
<i>Higuchi is Kira.</i>

204
00:12:58,695 --> 00:12:59,862
<i>That's horrible...</i>

205
00:13:10,832 --> 00:13:13,126
Misa-Misa sure is late...

206
00:13:16,087 --> 00:13:17,380
They're back!

207
00:13:17,547 --> 00:13:18,548
Hey!

208
00:13:19,924 --> 00:13:22,218
I am so tired.

209
00:13:22,635 --> 00:13:23,636
Hey...

210
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,762
How was it?

211
00:13:25,054 --> 00:13:29,017
Yotsuba has hired Misa
to appear in their ads.

212
00:13:29,684 --> 00:13:31,894
I see. That's great.

213
00:13:32,353 --> 00:13:34,731
Once I told them
my cell phone number,

214
00:13:34,897 --> 00:13:39,360
I got asked out
by three of the seven already.

215
00:13:39,527 --> 00:13:40,611
What?

216
00:13:40,862 --> 00:13:43,740
I just have to accept
and investigate them, right?

217
00:13:43,906 --> 00:13:45,325
It's going exactly as planned.

218
00:13:45,491 --> 00:13:47,452
No, the plan has been cancelled.

219
00:13:48,244 --> 00:13:51,414
Why? It's been going so well...

220
00:13:51,706 --> 00:13:53,875
You'll be in danger if we do this.

221
00:13:54,709 --> 00:13:56,961
I won't stop you from appearing
in any of their commercials,

222
00:13:57,045 --> 00:14:00,048
but from now on, deny that you were
suspected of being the Second Kira

223
00:14:00,131 --> 00:14:02,008
and that you were
detained by L.

224
00:14:02,592 --> 00:14:04,761
Mogi will be your bodyguard...

225
00:14:05,094 --> 00:14:06,846
and you will just be
an entertainer.

226
00:14:10,224 --> 00:14:13,478
If that's what you say,
then that's what I'll do...

227
00:14:16,105 --> 00:14:19,067
Well, I'm tired and tomorrow's shoot
is early in the morning,

228
00:14:19,150 --> 00:14:20,234
so I'm going to bed.

229
00:14:22,695 --> 00:14:25,782
<i>Thank you for worrying
about me, Light...</i>

230
00:14:26,282 --> 00:14:28,743
<i>But I've come up with a good plan!</i>

231
00:14:29,869 --> 00:14:31,829
<i>I'm gonna be of use to you!</i>

232
00:14:35,041 --> 00:14:37,085
